  "summary": "ocrodjvu is vulnerable to Arbitrary File Modification via symlink attack",
  "details": "ocrodjvu 0.4.6-1 on Debian GNU/Linux allows local users to modify arbitrary files via a symlink attack on temporary files that are generated when Cuneiform is invoked as the OCR engine.",
